title: ArcGIS Portal Federation Status
agents: special
catalog: app/arcgis
license: GPL
distribution: custom

description:
 This check monitors the overall federation validation status returned by Portal.

 It is intended as a summary of the Portal federation state. Per-server federation
 details are exposed by the ArcGIS Federated Server checks.
item:
 This check has no item.
discovery:
 One service is discovered when Portal federation validation data is present.
